1.2.2 (April 2026)
=======
=> Fix two bugs where, depending on the location in the call stack of the
   shred where Rec was called:
   * Rec.auto() would save the file in the directory where Rec.ck was located
   * Rec calls would block the shred, rather than spork, and prevent the shred
     from advancing.